	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You hold a moldavite crystal, casting a container into the ethereal plane with a spell, hiding the chest from all but the most skilled of magicians.</em></p><p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require a container no larger than a 5 ft. cube, as well as a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Py0I1npvYDW0caIr]{Moldavite Crystal}, typically valued at 150 gold. Neither component is consumed when you cast the spell.</p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p>You cast a chest and all its contents into the ethereal plane, where it is nearly impossible to reach it.</p></li><li><p>The chest can contain up to 12 cubic feet of non-living material. Living material is harmlessly left behind.</p></li><li><p>When the chest is on the ethereal plane, any creature who knows this spell can touch the same moldavite to call the chest back to their current position. You must then cast the spell again to send the chest back.</p></li><li><p>You cannot use a moldavite already linked to a secret chest on the ethereal plane.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>If the moldavite is destroyed, the chest is lost in the ethereal plane, where it is nearly impossible to find.</em></p>",
